.TH simple_shell 1 "2023-07-26" "Linux" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple command line interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
simple_shell [options] [command]
.SH DESCRIPTION
simple_shell is a simple command line interpreter that can be used to run commands.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-h\fR
Displays help information.
.TP
\fB-v\fR
Displays the version of the simple_shell.
.SH EXAMPLES
To run the `ls` command, you would type the following:

simple_shell ls

To display the help information, you would type the following:

simple_shell -h

To display the version of the simple_shell, you would type the following:

simple_shell -v

.SH SEE ALSO
bash, sh
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
